&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Negotiate: &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Negotiate and draft a diverse array of contracts including vendor agreements, license agreements, technology agreements, and derivative contracts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
