&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ProShares is seeking a detail-oriented and highly organized Content Marketing Specialist to support the development, coordination, and review of marketing content across the organization. In this role, you’ll help move content through the full editorial and approval process, working closely with members of the Content Marketing team, internal subject matter experts, compliance, and other key stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is a strong communicator with excellent attention to detail, sound editorial judgment, and the ability to manage multiple projects in a deadline-driven environment. Copy editing experience is a plus, as is experience working in a content, editorial, marketing, or financial services environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent opportunity for someone looking to grow their experience in content marketing at a leading financial firm, while gaining hands-on exposure to investment-related communications, editorial workflows, and regulatory review processes.&lt;/p&gt;
