&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Content Coordination&lt;/strong&gt;: Support the day-to-day management of content marketing projects, helping ensure materials move efficiently through drafting, editing, review, approval, and publication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Editorial Support&lt;/strong&gt;: Assist with reviewing, proofreading, formatting, and copy editing a range of marketing materials, including articles, emails, web content, presentations, product-related materials, and other investor communications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Management&lt;/strong&gt;: Track content deliverables, deadlines, stakeholder feedback, and approvals to help ensure projects remain organized and on schedule.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance Review Support&lt;/strong&gt;: Help prepare and submit materials for compliance review, coordinate revisions, track comments, and ensure final materials are approved before use.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;: Work closely with members of marketing, investment strategy, product, compliance, legal, sales, and other internal partners to support content development and execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Content Maintenance&lt;/strong&gt;: Assist with updating existing materials to reflect current messaging, data, regulatory requirements, and brand standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quality Control&lt;/strong&gt;: Review materials for accuracy, consistency, grammar, style, formatting, and alignment with ProShares’ brand voice and editorial standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Workflow and Documentation&lt;/strong&gt;: Help maintain project trackers, editorial calendars, content inventories, and related documentation to support transparency and accountability across the content process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other duties and responsibilities as assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
