&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Marketing, Communications, Journalism, English, Business, Finance, or related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1-3 years of experience in content marketing, editorial, communications, marketing, or a related field, ideally in financial services, asset management, or another regul

